<item>
            <title>[PDFBOX-2384] ExtractText should default to UTF-8</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-2384</link>
                <project id="12310760" key="PDFBOX">PDFBox</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;ExtractText (and perhaps also PDFTextStripper) should default to UTF-8, which is what most people expect. There have been two long-standing open issues &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-755&quot; title=&quot;Wrong translation of capital letters with combining diacritics&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-755&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-755&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-970&quot; title=&quot;TeX-created ligatures and umlauts are not recognised&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-970&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-970&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, because of not using having a good default.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve escalated this to a bug, see the first comment.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
